EN: The development zone of this city has advanced production technology.

ZH: 我们需要更多的资金来支持开发区的建设。
EN: We need more funds to support the construction of the development zone.

ZH: 开发区的环境保护工作得到了重视。
EN: Environmental protection in the development zone has been given priority.

