EN: The transportation conditions in the development zone have been continuously improving.

ZH: 这次会议的主题是关于开发区的规划。
EN: The theme of this meeting is about the planning of the development zone.

ZH: 开发区的企业品牌影响力逐渐扩大。
EN: The brand influence of enterprises in the development zone is gradually expanding.

